Greeting Program 

Depending upon the time you will greet your friends 

four modules - good Morning - Before 11 AM 
                Good Afternoon - Till 5 pm 
                Good Evening -   till 8 pm 
                Good Night - For rest of the time 

5 python files - goodMorning.py --> Greet --> Print("Hi Good Morning")
                goodAfternoon.py --> Greet --> Print("Hi Good Afternoon")